text:
1. Raise arms overhead
2. Lower arms to chest level
3. Extend arms forward
4. Shift weight to one leg
5. Lift opposite leg
6. Step forward with lifted leg
7. Shift weight to the front leg
8. Lower the lifted leg
9. Repeat steps 4-8 with the other leg
10. Rotate upper body to the side
11. Extend arms to the side
12. Rotate upper body to the other side
13. Repeat steps 10-12 in the opposite direction
14. Bring arms back to chest level
15. Lower arms to the sides
16. Relax the body and breathe deeply
